name: Photographers Gift Pack!
description:
This photograpers pack is full of goodies! With this set you will get some of your favorite vintage u creation items all in one for a great price!

In this pack you will get,

A Camera Necklace - your choice of gem
A newborn halo in purple or blue
Stella headband
Swoon headband

How great is this! something for everyone 

After purchase, please leave in a note during paypal checkout which color gem you would like for your necklace, and which color halo you would like - you can scroll through the shop to see what every one of the products included looks like :)

Thank you!!

Please allow one week before shipment

name: Vintage Camera Necklace
description:
Be the envy of every photographer with this vintage camera necklace. This Tibetan silver necklace can come with your choice of a red gem, clear, soft pink or purple. If you wish to have plain charm just select "no gem please" below. 


* All materials are lead free *


Price is $20.00 and that includes Free Shipping within the US!

name: Stella
description:
Stella is a handmade flower with a cream top and white french netting.. the colors are almost blue water color.. it's beautiful 

newborn to adult size

name: Dream A Dream Action Set
description:
Dream A Dream is a sweet little action set that can be used on any photo.. It works great on those creamy newborn pictures, as well as a nice pop for outdoor photos. 

This set includes 3 actions 

- Sweet Dreams
- Vintage Dream
- Dreamy Skin 


This set was created in CS3 and has been tested in Elements 7. Basic knowledge of actions is suggested to get the most use out of these. 


This set will be emailed to you within 24 hours after payment

name: 12x18 Dry Erase Board Template
description:
This is a Photoshop template created in CS5 but tested in CS3 for a 12x18 dry erase board. You can edit anything you want with this template, colors, etc. I created this template for my new studio, that way I can write down my sessions, and reminders and erase when the month is over. This template has been created to be printed at Millers Photo Lab. 

File will be sent to you within 24 hours but usually right after payment is received
